annotationA: DNA repair protein Rad51 homolog; Spindle A forms a filament on single-stranded DNA, does a homology search of double-stranded DNA, and catalyzes strand exchange, swapping the single-strand DNA in and displacing the partner of the complementary strand
annotationB: Mlh1, isoform A; Mismatched DNA binding; ATP binding; MutSalpha complex binding; single-stranded DNA binding; ATPase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: reciprocal meiotic recombination; mismatch repair
